a.n: This Time with Alan Partridge I (5/6)

p.k: A special programme focusing on the delicate issue of the #MeToo movement and a chance for Alan to show off his broadcasting chops. United Kingdom (2019). Cast: Steve Coogan, Susannah Fielding, Felicity Montagu, Tim Key, Cariad Lloyd. Director: Neil Gibbons, Rob Gibbons.
